                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            ICCAD '11: Proceedings of the International Conference on Computer-Aided DesignNovember 2011, pp 4047
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            A low-power architecture for an on-chip multi-banked video memory for motion and disparity
                  estimation in Multiview Video Coding is proposed. The memory organization (size, banks,
                  sectors, etc.) is driven by an extensive analysis of memory-usage behavior ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              An evaluation of the internal quality of business applications: does size matter?
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Bill Curtis, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Jay Sappidi, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Jitendra Subramanyam
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              ICSE '11: Proceedings of the 33rd International Conference on Software EngineeringMay 2011, pp 711715https://doi.org/10.1145/1985793.1985893
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              This study summarizes results of a study of the internal, structural quality of 288
                  business applications comprising 108 million lines of code collected from 75 companies
                  in 8 industry segments. These applications were submitted to a static analysis ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                An effective fusion and tile size model for optimizing image processing pipelines
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Abhinav Jangda, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Uday Bondhugula
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                PPoPP '18: Proceedings of the 23rd ACM SIGPLAN Symposium on Principles and Practice of Parallel
                     ProgrammingFebruary 2018, pp 261275https://doi.org/10.1145/3178487.3178507
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Effective models for fusion of loop nests continue to remain a challenge in both general-purpose
                  and domain-specific language (DSL) compilers. The difficulty often arises from the
                  combinatorial explosion of grouping choices and their interaction with ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Automatic size and variance determination for better surface splatting quality on
                     close-up view
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • Kar-Weng Ban
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  VRCAI '11: Proceedings of the 10th International Conference on Virtual Reality Continuum and
                     Its Applications in IndustryDecember 2011, pp 249256https://doi.org/10.1145/2087756.2087792
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Surface splatting has been proven to be a viable alternative to traditional polygon
                  rendering for highly detailed models. In terms of rendering performance, surface splatting
                  has surpassed polygon rendering when it fully exploits today's graphics ...


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Automatic verification of linear controller software
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • Miroslav Pajic, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • Junkil Park, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • Insup Lee, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • George J. Pappas, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • Oleg Sokolsky
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    EMSOFT '15: Proceedings of the 12th International Conference on Embedded SoftwareOctober 2015, pp 217226
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    We consider the problem of verification of software implementations of linear time-invariant
                  controllers. Commonly, different implementations use different representations of
                  the controller's state, for example due to optimizations in a third-party code ...

     
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Analyzing the performance of code-copying virtual machines
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • Gregory B. Prokopski, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • Clark Verbrugge
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      OOPSLA '08: Proceedings of the 23rd ACM SIGPLAN conference on Object-oriented programming systems
                     languages and applicationsOctober 2008, pp 403422https://doi.org/10.1145/1449764.1449796
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Many popular programming languages use interpreter-based execution for portability,
                  supporting dynamic or reflective properties, and ease of implementation. Code-copying is an optimization technique for interpreters that reduces the performance gap ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Code-based cache partitioning for improving hardware cache performance
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • Junghoon Kim, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • Inhyuk Kim, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • Young Ik Eom
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        ICUIMC '12: Proceedings of the 6th International Conference on Ubiquitous Information Management
                     and CommunicationFebruary 2012, Article No.: 42, pp 15https://doi.org/10.1145/2184751.2184803
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Recently, improving hardware cache performance is getting more important, because
                  the performance gap between processor and memory has caused "memory wall" problem.
                  Most cache designs are based on the LRU replacement policy which is effective for
                  high-...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Dynamically tuning the population size in particle swarm optimization
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • Andr L. V. Coelho, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • Daniel G. de Oliveira
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          SAC '08: Proceedings of the 2008 ACM symposium on Applied computingMarch 2008, pp 17821787https://doi.org/10.1145/1363686.1364115
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          In this paper, we investigate the benefits of dynamically varying the population size
                  in the Particle Swarm Optimization (PSO) model. For this purpose, two well-known population
                  resizing techniques, originally developed for Genetic Algorithms (GAs), ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            One-size-fits-none?: improving test generation using context-optimized fitness functions
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • Gregory Gay
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            SBST '19: Proceedings of the 12th International Workshop on Search-Based Software TestingMay 2019, pp 34https://doi.org/10.1109/SBST.2019.000-1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Current approaches to search-based test case generation have yielded limited results
                  in terms of human-competitiveness. However, effective search-based test generation
                  relies on the selection of the correct fitness functions---feedback mechanisms---for
                  ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Size Matters: Improving the Performance of Small Files in Hadoop
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Salman Niazi, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Mikael Ronstrm, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Seif Haridi, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Jim Dowling
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Middleware '18: Proceedings of the 19th International Middleware ConferenceNovember 2018, pp 2639https://doi.org/10.1145/3274808.3274811
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              The Hadoop Distributed File System (HDFS) is designed to handle massive amounts of
                  data, preferably stored in very large files. The poor performance of HDFS in managing
                  small files has long been a bane of the Hadoop community. In many production ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Beating OPT with Statistical Clairvoyance and Variable Size Caching

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      On the diffusion of test smells in automatically generated test code: an empirical study

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Code Spartanization: one rational approach for resolving religious style wars
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • Yossi Gil, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • Matteo Orr
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          SAC '17: Proceedings of the Symposium on Applied ComputingApril 2017, pp 16151622https://doi.org/10.1145/3019612.3019748
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Spartan programming is a coding style which tries to minimize the elements of code,
                  like in a laconic speech. In the context of code, the minimized elements of speech
                  include lines, characters, arguments, nesting use of ifs and whiles, etc. The style
                  is ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Optimizing application downtime through intelligent VM placement and migration in
                     cloud data centers
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Venkatesh Nandakumar,

                     EngineeringNovember 2015, pp 3544
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              As cloud data centres grow in size and complexity, hosted applications become increasingly
                  vulnerable to dynamically occurring infrastructure downtime periods caused by partial
                  infrastructure failures.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 Towards an autonomous bot for automatic source code refactoring
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Marvin Wyrich, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Justus Bogner
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                BotSE '19: Proceedings of the 1st International Workshop on Bots in Software EngineeringMay 2019, pp 2428https://doi.org/10.1109/BotSE.2019.00015
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Continuous refactoring is necessary to maintain source code quality and to cope with
                  technical debt. Since manual refactoring is inefficient and error-prone, various solutions
                  for automated refactoring have been proposed in the past. However, empirical ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  FBT: filled buffer technique to reduce code size for VLIW processors

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Study and Sizing of Stand-Alone Photovoltaic System Using PVsyst Software
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • Touahri Tahar, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        •

                  the amount of electrical energy produced by the photoelectric system. In this paper
                  we use the Pvsyst software for sizing and simulation of a stand-alone solar ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Application-specific memory partitioning for joint energy and lifetime optimization

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Automatic application of the category-partition method with loops support over functional
                     requirements

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              This paper extends previous works about the automatic generation of test cases. The
                  start point id the Category -Partition method and the extended use case pattern. This
                  paper describes the automatism of both techniques and extends them to manage loops
