                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Cache size in a cost model for heterogeneous skeletons
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Khari Armih, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • Greg Michaelson,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                HLPP '11: Proceedings of the fifth international workshop on High-level parallel programming
                     and applicationsSeptember 2011, pp 310https://doi.org/10.1145/2034751.2034755
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                High performance architectures are increasingly heterogeneous with shared and distributed
                  memory components. Programming such architectures is complicated and performance portability
                  is a major issue as the architectures evolve.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                This paper proposes a ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Performance Optimisation of the Parallel CFD Code MGLET across Different HPC Platforms

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  This paper presents the optimisation techniques implemented to run across four HPC
                  platforms the finite-volume computational fluid dynamics (CFD) code MGLET (Multi Grid
                  Large Eddy Turbulence). We analysed and applied refactoring to the parallel ...

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Optimal rate list decoding of folded algebraic-geometric codes over constant-sized
                     alphabets
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • Venkatesan Guruswami, 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • 
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • Chaoping Xing
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • 
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      SODA '14: Proceedings of the twenty-fifth annual ACM-SIAM symposium on Discrete algorithmsJanuary 2014, pp 18581866
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
               		
               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      We construct a new list-decodable family of asymptotically good algebraic-geometric
                  (AG) codes over fixed alphabets. The function fields underlying these codes are constructed
                  using class field theory, specifically Drinfeld modules of rank 1, and ...
